        # Scaffolding addon for gcdt to manage AWS Lambda functions 
        
        author: glomex SRE Team
        gcdt: https://github.com/glomex/gcdt
        
        Gru is an experimental and shameless copy of the chalice app.
        https://github.com/awslabs/chalice/blob/master/chalice/app.py
        
