        ## Running tests
        
        Please make sure to have good test coverage for your plugin so we can always make sure your plugin runs with the upcoming gcdt version.
        
        Run tests like so:
        
        ``` bash
        $ python -m pytest -vv --cov-report term-missing tests/test_*
        ```
        
        
